13 assist them in the understanding of and execution of their duties and responsibilities to the
14 community school district. The Notwithstanding Title 20-A, section 1651, subsection 4,
15 the community school district may not vote in accordance with Title 20-A, section 1651,
16 subsection 4 to have the district school committee perform the duties of the board of
